    "department": "Sales",
    "description": "🏥 WHAT WE DO\n\nAt Vitalize, we are building the OS for hospital operations, starting with staffing \u0026 scheduling optimization.\n\nLabor is 60% of the P\u0026L of American healthcare. However, hospital’s core processes to manage and optimize labor live on paper, spreadsheets, or through departments of 20+ FTEs. Vitalizes transforms these processes from painstakingly tedious to autonomous, freeing up thousands of hours and reducing labor costs by 8-figures.\n\n\n🪓 ABOUT THE ROLE\n\nWe're approaching near 8-figures in ARR and are on track to be the fastest growing company in enterprise healthcare. We’re hiring for a Founding AE to help us build the best enterprise GTM motion in healthcare and scale Vitalize take us from $10M to $100M in ARR. You’ll be selling our software to health systems and work directly with our CEO to build Vitalize Care’s GTM organization.\n\n\n🥇 SKILLS\n\n - 2+ years of enterprise sales experience.\n\n - Proven track record of closing high 6 figure and 7 figure enterprise contracts.\n\n - Ability to “make something out of nothing.” We’re excited about individuals who identify creative avenues to identify leads and scale our pipeline.\n\n - Nice to Have Experiences: experience working with health systems, experience at seed or Series A stage startups\n\n\n📍 LOCATION\n\n - In-Person, San Francisco, CA 🌉\n\n - Travel to conferences and potential customer sites up to 50% of days\n\n\n🙌 BENEFITS\n\n - Medical, dental, and vision insurance\n\n - 401k and 401k match\n\n - Unlimited PTO\n\n - Bi-annual company retreats\n\n - Reimbursement for gym subscription (~$100 per month)\n\n - Reimbursement for BayWheels membership/new bike and Ubers\n\n - In-office meals",
